🚀 What Comes Next (Beyond Finance)

With AFC-001 through AFC-016 complete, your finance foundation is largely covered. The next logical enterprise platforms are:

Treasury & ALM (Asset-Liability Management) — liquidity, funding, investments, interest rate risk, and regulatory ratios.
Enterprise Risk Management (ERM) — credit, operational, market, liquidity, compliance, and model risk.
Regulatory Compliance Platform — RBI/NBFC compliance, policy management, inspections, and obligations.
Enterprise Data Warehouse & BI — unified analytics, dashboards, and executive reporting.
Enterprise AI Platform — copilots, predictive analytics, decision support, and intelligent automation across every module.

For an NBFC, I would implement Treasury & ALM next, because it directly complements the financial core and is essential for funding strategy, liquidity management, regulatory compliance, and profitability.